query:
SELECT 
  id,
  smshubActivationId,
  phoneNumber,
  LENGTH(smshubActivationId) as id_length,
  LENGTH(phoneNumber) as phone_length,
  serviceId,
  createdAt
FROM activations
WHERE serviceId = (SELECT id FROM services WHERE smshubCode = 'tg')
ORDER BY id DESC
LIMIT 1;
